FBIS4-31297 "dreeu110_d_94005" FBIS-EEU-94-110 Daily Report 3 Jun 1994 SLOVAKIA Union Leaders Deny Electoral Pact With HZDS Union Leaders Deny Electoral Pact With HZDS AU0706121494 Bratislava SME in Slovak 3 Jun 94 p 1 AU0706121494 Bratislava SME Slovak BFN [Article by "bor": "The Confederation of Trade Unions Will Not Go Into the Elections With the Movement for a Democratic Slovakia"] [Text] Alojz Englis, president of the Confederation of Trade Unions [KOZ], Vladimir Stevko, vice president of KOZ, and J. Blahak yesterday denied reports that the KOZ leadership would go into the elections "in the colors of the Movement for a Democratic Slovakia [HZDS]." Even if they received such an offer, they would not consider it, they said.
